{"tid":864014,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"一打J就好易病，有咩解決方法？","createTime":"2018-10-16T02:38:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T11:59:33.000Z","uid":103264,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"eb42c6d899f2e48c7bcca30b9c79aad98f38624c","tid":864014,"uid":103264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T02:38:56.000Z","msg":"今年23歲<br />\n次次一打完J，第二日就頭痛同喉嚨痛<br />\n之後通常要食傷風藥先好番，搞個四五日<br />\n<br />\n咁樣既狀況維持左一兩年<br />\n搞到依家成日唔敢打J<br />\n一個月先打一次，但係都會病<br />\n<br />\n睇過兩個西醫一個中醫，都係叫我做多D運動，增強身體抵抗力<br />\n但係我間唔中有行山同跳繩，又無咩不良嗜好<br />\n<br />\n依家<br />\n想戒J但係又戒唔到<br />\n想打J但係又唔敢打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有咩解決方法？"},{"pid":"d817ea216af1139d7f6139ee6ffba8df92901ead","tid":864014,"uid":209389,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T02:39:41.000Z","msg":"切左佢"},{"pid":"ef2af8c53c668a7dd730cf7219d75fe54ef73178","tid":864014,"uid":212685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T02:39:47.000Z","msg":"Chasity Cage幫到你."},{"pid":"b335d25b6010f8be5ac4d5f30b80d90a27e17484","tid":864014,"uid":37746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T02:40:03.000Z","msg":"打兩次咪唔易病"},{"pid":"0fbfdee987c17a16dd11cf1f74b902c4bccaaa42","tid":864014,"uid":141630,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T02:40:17.000Z","msg":"唔好打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為身體已經同你講緊再打就出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b86018b821bfde8fe48d5f3052f874676af753","tid":864014,"uid":117552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T02:41:21.000Z","msg":"跑步啦"},{"pid":"1b76db4c4a231367cdb3921d891b90d6cea3bac8","tid":864014,"uid":166785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T02:42:40.000Z","msg":"自宮"},{"pid":"ae048cd146959ff6785cae615071d9fc036f7d5f","tid":864014,"uid":216943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci